        <item>
          <title>11 seed Texas upsets No 3 Gonzaga in March Madness tournament to advance to the Sweet 16</title>
          <description><![CDATA[The 11th-seeded Texas Longhorns advanced to the Sweet 16 for just the second time since 2008 after a 74-68 upset win over No. 3 Gonzaga, which suffered back-to-back second-round exits.]]></description>
